# Pizza_Sales_Dashboard

# Project Description
A dynamic Excel-based dashboard that visualizes pizza sales data, built as part of a BI assignment. It helps in understanding sales performance across various metrics like revenue, best sellers, order trends, and more.

# Key Features
Interactive Excel Dashboard using Pivot Tables and Charts
Key KPIs: Total Revenue, Total Orders, Average Order Value
Time Series Trend Analysis
Best and Worst Performing Pizzas
Category-wise and Size-wise Breakdown
Data Cleaning and Formatting

# Skills & Tools Used
Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
Pivot Charts
Slicers
Data Cleaning
Dashboard Design
